data.description: Gorgeous 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Cabin in Cul-de-sac that backs up to stream with a deep wrap around covered porch and a private balcony off the master suite. Home has hardwood flooring throughout, large secondary bedrooms and lots of storage space. The kitchen has granite countertops, stained wooden cabinets and all stainless steel appliances. The Great room has vaulted ceilings and a wood burning fireplace with gas starter. Master suite is oversized and the master bath has separate tub in shower with walk in closets. Hardwood floors are refinished. Hurry this peaceful mountain home will not last long.
